typedef struct DPU_StaticClutterProc_ScratchBuf_t DPU_StaticClutterProc_ScratchBuf

Scratch buffer used by DPU.

The structure defines the scratch buffer interface, including size and data pointer. This buffer should be allocated from internal memory (TCMB if running on R4F and L2/L1 SRAM on DSP) as the clutter removal algorithm will be performed on data sitting on this buffer.

typedef struct DPU_StaticClutterProc_StaticConfig_t DPU_StaticClutterProc_StaticConfig

Doppler DPU static configuration parameters.

The structure is used to hold the static configuration parameters for the Doppler DPU
